            <title>[DERBY-6649] Meaningless permissions granted to sysinfo.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6649</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The server.policy and template.policy files grant the following meaningless permissions in every block related to sysinfo:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  permission java.io.FilePermission &quot;java.runtime.version&quot;, &quot;read&quot;;&lt;br/&gt;
  permission java.io.FilePermission &quot;java.fullversion&quot;, &quot;read&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
